&gt;ahau-graphql-server&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;A GraphQL endpoint which made UI dev more accessible for all our developers&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Code within ƒÄhau:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;an algorithm for progressively loading huge family trees (5000+ people)
smoothly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;export function which converts a D3 tree into an SVG with embedded images
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;this was to support a community member to create an updated whakapapa 10
meters wide, 2 meters high, including 1200 people.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>Dark Crystal</title><link>https://mixmix.nz/p/dark-crystal/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Jul 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mixmix.nz/p/dark-crystal/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://mixmix.nz/p/dark-crystal/logo.jpeg" alt="Featured image of post Dark Crystal" /&gt;&lt;h2 id="about"&gt;About
