&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is the project I have contributed the most to in my life. It&amp;rsquo;s a p2p
replicating database, and a solarpunk community that grew up around and through
it. I&amp;rsquo;ve made life-long friends and built bridges spanning almost every
continent and honestly it&amp;rsquo;s a challenge hard to summarize.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;#x1f6a7; Please feel free to direct queries to me about what you&amp;rsquo;d like
to know more about&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id="things-ive-done"&gt;Things I&amp;rsquo;ve done
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Here&amp;rsquo;s an incomplete summary of the many roles/ projects/ things I did:&lt;/p&gt;
