&gt;dogfooding&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ran distributed strategy setting process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wrote many libraries + plugins&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Developed many applications on top of Scuttlebutt
