&lt;li&gt;TikTak&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Patchbay&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Co-designed new cryptographic primitives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Created learning resources + documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ran an &lt;a class="link" href="https://one.camp.scuttlebutt.nz/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;international conference&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ran grant process distributing ~$500K&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Administered Maintenance and Grant-writing funds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gave conference &lt;a class="link" href="https://mixmix.nz/categories/talks/" &gt;talks&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
